text: The women's artistic individual all-around gymnastic event at the 2019 Pan American Games was held on July 29 at the Polideportivo Villa el Salvador in Lima, Peru. Ellie Black of Canada successfully defended her title from the 2015 Pan American Games. ==Schedule== All times are Peru Time (UTC-5). {| class="wikitable" ! Date ! Time !
